cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.EM, cs.Medical Imaging, cs.SY

Reasoning: 
1. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - This paper discusses the design and implementation of a wireless network for medical applications, which falls under the scope of networking and internet architecture. 
2. cs.IT (Information Theory) - The paper discusses the use of wireless communication and low-power MAC protocols, which are related to information theory. 
3. cs.EM (Electromagnetics) - The paper discusses in-body antenna design, which falls under the scope of electromagnetics. 
4. cs.Medical Imaging - The paper discusses the use of wireless body area networks for medical applications, which includes medical imaging. 
5. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper discusses the design and implementation of a system for wireless body area networks, which falls under the scope of systems and control.
